cohortName: [PL 140168001] Psoriasis referent concept incident cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants with >=365d prior observation
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (140168) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 140168002] Psoriasis referent concept prevalent cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (140168) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 140168003] Psoriasis at first diagnosis (no history of Psoriasis)
logicDescription: Psoriasis at first diagnosis with 365 days continuous observation, with no history of psoriasis. Cohort exit is the end of continuous observable time for the person.

cohortName: [PL 140168004] Psoriasis, exclude parapsoriasis and less common psoriasis subtypes specifically guttate psoriasis, generalized pustular psoriasis
logicDescription: Psoriasis at first diagnosis with 365 days continuous observation. Exclude persons with parapsoriasis, guttate psoriasis, generalized pustular psoriasis at any time. Cohort exit is the end of continuous observable time for the person.

cohortName: [PL 140168005] Psoriasis excluding Guttate Psoriasis and Palmoplantar Pustulosis
logicDescription: Psoriasis at first diagnosis with 365 days continuous observation. Exclude persons with guttate psoriasis and palmoplantar pustuolosis at any time. Cohort exit is the end of continuous observable time for the person.
